&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And so, we recorded the user&amp;rsquo;s data. This example shows a very simplified example, in a good way, you need to store intermediate data and user states in a database, but today we are working with a bot, not databases. The final touch â€“ we will ask users to confirm that everything is entered correctly, and not just like that, but with buttons! To do this, edit the code of the get_age method a little&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;get_age&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;
